		<element kind="textField" uuid="694efdaa-2442-400e-9033-5747e013e509" x="1" y="126" width="378" height="8" forecolor="#8C1915" fontSize="6.0" bold="true" hTextAlign="Center" vTextAlign="Middle">
			<expression><![CDATA["Thank you, " + $F{name} + " for choosing " +$F{reg_name}]]></expression>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="d7f94079-b494-4f89-8f50-9dff7adc9adb" x="15" y="108" width="350" height="17" fontSize="6.0" bold="true">
			<text><![CDATA[ No cash refund policy: No monetary refunds will be given for any reason, though alternative  refunds may be offered, such as store credit or exchanges]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="2195d997-39d9-4c61-8786-2f731c4e96e6" x="15" y="92" width="335" height="16" fontSize="6.0" bold="true">
			<text><![CDATA[No refunds. Exchange only: Customers may exchange items they wish to return, but they cannot get a monetary refund]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="bcb3c368-f0b2-43c0-9406-68eba56dce70" x="15" y="75" width="350" height="17" fontSize="6.0" bold="true">
			<text><![CDATA[All sales are final : Once customers make a purchase, they will not be able to return that item for a replacement or refund. These policies typically apply to clearance and sale items.]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="9a458e35-6bfd-40db-a58c-cb6c81d79831" x="15" y="64" width="350" height="10" fontSize="6.0">
			<text><![CDATA[ If any advance is paid for this invoice this should be treated as a Receipt of advance.]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="0afa37a0-420d-4e7a-a50a-e22bef84cfe2" x="15" y="54" width="350" height="10" fontSize="6.0">
			<text><![CDATA[If this invoice is fully paid, it should be treated as a receipt of full payment]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="0bc76572-b896-4a7e-a19c-42be9bda716f" x="15" y="44" width="350" height="10" fontSize="6.0">
			<text><![CDATA[Once booked, orders cannot be cancelled]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="8a03cc07-c640-45f6-9505-5602acec9900" x="15" y="34" width="350" height="10" fontSize="6.0">
			<text><![CDATA[Repair & adjustments of frames at customers' risk.]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="72c5d1d1-344b-4616-b150-8d9b472ae2f9" x="15" y="24" width="350" height="10" fontSize="6.0" bold="true">
			<text><![CDATA[Spectacles will be released after settling the full amount]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="5e5b915d-b351-461d-bfdc-251074213ace" x="15" y="14" width="350" height="10" fontSize="6.0" hTextAlign="Left" vTextAlign="Middle">
			<text><![CDATA[Please collect your spectacle within 90 days, otherwise, the order will be cancelled.]]></text>
		</element>
	</pageFooter>
